Hussain Industries (established 1994) is one of the largest textile manufacturers in Pakistan and is an export-oriented company of Pakistan. Located in Pakistan’s largest cotton-growing area of Multan, this co-proprietorship firm (partnership) is owned equally by two parties − CEO Ghulam Hussain and a group consisting of Muhammad Ajmal Hameed, Shahid Hameed, Tajammal Hameed, and Muhammad Amir. Its business office is also located in Karachi, Pakistan.
